# Physics for Games

## Velocity & Acceleration

```javascript
class Entity {
    constructor(x, y) {
        this.x = x; this.y = y;
        this.vx = 0; this.vy = 0; // velocity
        this.ax = 0; this.ay = 0; // acceleration
    }

    update(dt) {
        // Apply acceleration
        this.vx += this.ax * dt;
        this.vy += this.ay * dt;

        // Apply velocity
        this.x += this.vx * dt;
        this.y += this.vy * dt;
    }
}
```

## Gravity

```javascript
const GRAVITY = 980; // pixels/secÂ²

update(dt) {
    this.vy += GRAVITY * dt;
    this.y += this.vy * dt;

    // Ground collision
    if (this.y >= groundY) {
        this.y = groundY;
        this.vy = 0;
    }
}
```

## Friction

```javascript
const FRICTION = 0.9; // 10% slowdown per frame

update(dt) {
    this.vx *= Math.pow(FRICTION, dt * 60); // Frame-independent
}
```

## Jumping

```javascript
jump() {
    if (this.isOnGround) {
        this.vy = -500; // Negative = up
    }
}
```
